name: SXZ Jill Valentine - Sasha Zotova / Julia Voth [ Resident Evil ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with clip skip 2.

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5
3. badhandv4
Recommended extensions:
1. AutoChar
2. AfterDetailer
Strength 0.6-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

In last version you may use jillvoth for RE1 look (blue military uniform, blue eyes, beret, Julia Voth) or zotovalentine for look from RE 3 Remake (blue tank top, sholder holster, Sasha Zotova). If you choose one of them, add another to negative prompt. But unfortunately you can't get exact face of Sasha Zotova in last version, so if you want LORA only with her, download specific version.

Also you may add blue military uniform, shirt, beret, shoulder pads, black pants in positive prompt for RE1 look.

Also you may add blue tank top, shoulder holster, black skirt, sweater around waist in positive prompt for RE3 look.

Also you may improve it with negative prompt: loli, kid, child, old, young, sweat, wet skin

Please share your feedback.
